About 60 or 70 years ago,

3
00:00:02,688 --> 00:00:04,080
when people were asked

4
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:07,122
to imagine how the year 2020 would look,

5
00:00:07,551 --> 00:00:10,694
people imagined futuristic looking cities.

6
00:00:10,694 --> 00:00:12,789
Hoverboards.

7
00:00:12,789 --> 00:00:14,728
Cars flying in the sky.

8
00:00:15,243 --> 00:00:17,983
Flying cars would have become a reality.

9
00:00:17,983 --> 00:00:20,272
But unfortunately, it didn't happen.

10
