but this is so compact,

155
00:06:24,555 --> 00:06:27,565
so small that it can land on your roof

156
00:06:27,565 --> 00:06:30,304
and take off from your neighbourhood garden as well.

157
00:06:30,304 --> 00:06:31,916
To keep it lightweight,

158
00:06:31,916 --> 00:06:34,059
its frame is made of aluminium.

159
00:06:34,059 --> 00:06:37,074
And it weighs only 86kg.

160
00:06:37,074 --> 00:06:38,408
It is very light.

161
00:06:38,408 --> 00:06:39,796
And the person sitting in it,

162
